{"tid":1954112,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「纖維化」的心 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-04-01T14:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T14:48:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4be3d2f36c62370c5cb1cd7fb6be27990d3c855","tid":1954112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:46:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200401/20891227/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200401%2F20891227%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=85545423\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200401%2F20891227%2F&h=6671a358\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200401/20891227/</a><br />\n<br />\n「纖維化」的心 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200401/large/1585639062_fefd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200401%2Flarge%2F1585639062_fefd.jpg&h=70952412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n日本殿堂級喜劇演員志村健，是他《志村動物園》中「阿笨契爺」，出道近40年，一雙粗眉比本港滑稽紋眉政客有性格，受歡迎，即使是經典的「怪叔叔」亦不會乞人憎。<br />\n<br />\n他日前在東京一醫院中病逝，享年70歲，與他合作過的藝人和網友紛紛哀傷悼念。喜劇天王死因是感染武漢肺炎，如同全球78萬人受病毒感染，3萬多人死亡一樣無辜，因中國隱瞞疫情，病毒迅速擴散，全球大流行，承擔及陪葬&hellip;&hellip;當大家哀悼大師殞落時，不少大陸網軍偷偷翻牆，在維基百科上竄改死因，把「中國武漢肺炎」改成「台灣肺炎」，指鹿為馬，行為卑劣。<br />\n<br />\n一場災難性的瘟疫，暴露了人性的醜惡，黑白是非不分，中國大陸是毒源，但諉過嫁禍，還聲稱「援助」受害國，但荷蘭、法國收到的口罩檢測後確定是用不得的次貨，急須回收；西班牙採購的快速試劑準確度只2、3成；說是「送予」意大利的800萬個口罩，原來貴賣，每個港幣$14.5&hellip;&hellip;發國難財就別裝慈善了，但強國人會有羞恥心嗎？「大災星」搖身變成「救世主」，被洗腦的強國人更驕傲了。<br />\n<br />\n武肺不但令病者的肺纖維化，還令暫時未病者的心纖維化，再也沒有人性，且一直差下去&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"46909fb3e87edcc3d6579a099b8cdd83aec993fe","tid":1954112,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"心玻璃纖維化"},{"pid":"55cab015e936e83f4cc4ea55248c3a5df17ebcc4","tid":1954112,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"[理論]如何借藍絲五毛去擴大我哋嘅勢力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}